OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778573162
OL,3,CTeaching assistant jailed after
OL,4,C'hitting, pinching and spitting' at
OL,5,Cpupils
OL,7,FWatch: Danuska Pullia tells Kent
OL,8,FPolice she spat at a child, and
OL,9,Fpinched the nose of another.
OL,11,FA teaching assistant, who was trusted
OL,12,Fto look after vulnerable children, but
OL,13,Finstead, hit, pinched and spat at
OL,14,Fthem, has been jailed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
