PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778573162
OL,3,CTeaching assistant jailed after
OL,4,C'hitting, pinching and spitting' at
OL,5,Cpupils
OL,7,FDanuska Pullia, 47, was found guilty
OL,8,Fof child cruelty after a police
OL,9,Finvestigation found she was a "danger
OL,10,Fto children" and had 'utterly failed'
OL,11,Fin caring for pupils at her school in
OL,12,FSittingbourne between September 2021
OL,13,Fand July 2023.
OL,15,FIn a voluntary interview, Pullia
OL,16,Fdenied most of the allegations or
OL,17,Fclaimed they didn't take place as
OL,18,Freported. But, during that interview
OL,19,Fshe admitted to officers that she spat
OL,20,Fat one child after the pupil spat at
OL,21,Fher.
OL,26,@qD@_OUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
