OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778573162
OL,3,CTeaching assistant jailed after
OL,4,C'hitting, pinching and spitting' at
OL,5,Cpupils
OL,7,FShe told officers: "She spat at me
OL,8,Ffirst time, I didn't react. She spat
OL,9,Fat me second time, I didn't react. I
OL,10,Fdon't know why I did it the third time
OL,11,Fthough, I can't remember."
OL,13,FKent Police then asked her: "So you're
OL,14,Fsaying that you spat in the child's
OL,15,Fface, but you can't remember why?"
OL,17,FPullia replied: "I can't remember why
OL,18,FI did it, no."
OL,20,FOfficers then asked: "So did you spit
OL,21,Fin her face or their face?"
OL,26,@oD@TOUsD@ZO]uD@]OUwD@bO]yD@QOUzD@NO]|D@
OL,26,AVOU}D@[O]
