FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778573162
OL,3,CTeaching assistant jailed after
OL,4,C'hitting, pinching and spitting' at
OL,5,Cpupils
OL,7,FShe replied: "I spat not really in her
OL,8,Fface, but I did spat. I don't know why
OL,9,FI did it, but I know she did it to
OL,10,Fmaybe twice and I did spat back, but I
OL,11,Fcan't remember at that time why I did
OL,12,Fit or what happened."
OL,14,FIn the same interview, Pullia also
OL,15,Fadmitted to pinching the nose of
OL,16,Fanother, as she attempted to remove
OL,17,Fplastic from their mouth.
OL,26,@oD@NOUtD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
