PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778573162
OL,3,CTeaching assistant jailed after
OL,4,C'hitting, pinching and spitting' at
OL,5,Cpupils
OL,7,F"I pinched the child's nose so I could
OL,8,Ftake the food out of his mouth. That
OL,9,Fwas a chocolate bar. I didn't really
OL,10,Fpinch his nose, I just did this so I
OL,11,Fcould take the chocolate bar," she
OL,12,Ftold officers.
OL,14,FWhen asked what training she had
OL,15,Freceived to make her think pinching a
OL,16,Fchild was okay, she replied 'none'.
OL,17,FITV Meridian has approached Kent
OL,18,FCounty Council for comment.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
