PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778573162
OL,3,CTeaching assistant jailed after
OL,4,C'hitting, pinching and spitting' at
OL,5,Cpupils
OL,7,FShe was charged with four counts of
OL,8,Fchild cruelty in December 2023, and
OL,9,Fpleaded not guilty.
OL,11,FFollowing a trial at Maidstone Crown
OL,12,FCourt, a jury unanimously found her
OL,13,Fguilty of all charges. Pullia, of
OL,14,FWhite Satin Close, Iwade, was
OL,15,Fsentenced on Friday 8 May 2026 to four
OL,16,Fyears in jail.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
