PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1778573162
OL,3,CTeaching assistant jailed after
OL,4,C'hitting, pinching and spitting' at
OL,5,Cpupils
OL,7,FInvestigating officer Detective
OL,8,FConstable Hollie Kent said: "Pullia
OL,9,Fwas entrusted with the care of
OL,10,Fvulnerable children and utterly failed
OL,11,Fin that responsibility.
OL,13,F"Her actions have had a lasting impact
OL,14,Fon her victims, many of whom weren't
OL,15,Fable to speak out for themselves as to
OL,16,Fwhat happened. We are very grateful to
OL,17,Fthe families and guardians of the
OL,18,Fchildren affected for their support
OL,19,Fthroughout our enquiries.
OL,26,@pD@]OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
